---

<BaseLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
>
  <!-- Open Graph / Social Sharing Meta Tags -->
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta property="og:type" content="music.song" />
    <meta property="og:title" content={`${title} — Troy Sybert`} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={fullCoverUrl} />
    <meta property="og:url" content={pageUrl} />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Voice of Repentance" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={`${title} — Troy Sybert`} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={description} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={fullCoverUrl} />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-vor-charcoal text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-20">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
        <!-- Album Art -->
        <div class="w-64 h-64 sm:w-72 sm:h-72 md:w-80 md:h-80 flex-shrink-0">
          <img
            src={coverImage}
            alt={`${title} album cover`}
            class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Title & Links -->
        <div class="text-center md:text-left flex-1">
          <p class="text-vor-gold font-heading text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">
            New Music
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">
            {title}
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 font-heading mb-2">
            Troy Sybert
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-body mb-8 max-w-md">
            {description}
          </p>

          <!-- Streaming Links -->
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 max-w-xs mx-auto md:mx-0">
            {links.map((link) => (
              <a
                href={link.url}
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class={`flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-3 rounded-full text-white font-heading font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide transition-all duration-200 ${link.color} ${link.hoverColor} hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-lg no-underline`}
              >
                <Fragment set:html={link.icon} />
                <span>Listen on {link.name}</span>
              </a>
            ))}
          </div>
          <a
            href="#watch"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400 font-heading hover:text-vor-gold transition-colors no-underline"
          >
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
            Or watch the video below without leaving this page
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Devotional -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16 text-center">
      <p class="text-vor-gold-dark font-heading text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">
        Devotional
      </p>
      <blockquote class="text-lg md:text-xl font-body italic text-vor-charcoal-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
        "Enter through the narrow gate. For wide is the gate and broad is the road that leads to destruction, and many enter through it. But small is the gate and narrow the road that leads to life, and only a few find it."
      </blockquote>
      <p class="text-sm font-heading font-semibold text-vor-gold-dark tracking-wide">
        — Matthew 7:13–14
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-vor-muted font-body leading-relaxed max-w-lg mx-auto">
        We all end up in our own "town called Nowhere" at some point — a place we built with our own plans, our own pride, our own version of control. But the gospel tells us something that pride never will: the way out isn't through trying harder. It's through surrender. Grace doesn't wait for you to find your way back. It meets you right where you are — broken, worn, and out of options — and says, <em class="text-vor-charcoal">"Son, it's time to leave this place."</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- YouTube Video Section -->
  <section id="watch" class="bg-vor-cream scroll-mt-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-vor-charcoal text-center mb-8">
        Watch the Video
      </h2>
      <div class="relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl shadow-lg" style="padding-bottom: 56.25%;">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/A-Xza8SbaIA"
          title="Town Called Nowhere — Voice of Repentance"
          class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Lyrics Section -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-vor-charcoal text-center mb-10">
        Lyrics
      </h2>

      <div class="font-body text-vor-charcoal-light text-base leading-relaxed space-y-8">
        <!-- Verse 1 -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-heading font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-vor-gold-dark mb-3">Verse 1</p>
          <p>I walked alone, head down, heart blind<br/>
          Chasing a peace I could never find<br/>
          Built my plans with trembling hands<br/>
          But they all gave way to life's demands</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pre-Chorus -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-heading font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-vor-gold-dark mb-3">Pre-Chorus</p>
          <p>Prayed to the sky but heard no sound<br/>
          Just the ache of silence coming down</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Chorus -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-heading font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-vor-gold-dark mb-3">Chorus</p>
          <p>Now I'm here in a town called Nowhere<br/>
          Every road led me back to despair<br/>
          I strayed from the path, the narrow gate<br/>
          Chose my will and called it fate<br/>
          He calls with mercy, He calls with grace:<br/>
          <em>"Son, it is time to leave this place."</em></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Verse 2 -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-heading font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-vor-gold-dark mb-3">Verse 2</p>
          <p>I took one step, then one more slow<br/>
          Didn't know the way, but had to go<br/>
          Left my pride by the welcome sign<br/>
          Prayed for His strength — I'm outta mine</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Pre-Chorus (Hopeful) -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-heading font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-vor-gold-dark mb-3">Pre-Chorus</p>
          <p>Now every breath feels a little more free<br/>
          Like He never stopped walking with me</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Repeat Chorus -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-heading font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-vor-gold-dark mb-3">Chorus</p>
          <p>Now I'm here in a town called Nowhere<br/>
          Every road led me back to despair<br/>
          I strayed from the path, the narrow gate<br/>
          Chose my will and called it fate<br/>
          He calls with mercy, He calls with grace:<br/>
          <em>"Son, it is time to leave this place."</em></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Bridge -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-heading font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-vor-gold-dark mb-3">Bridge</p>
          <p>He found me broken, worn and slow<br/>
          But mercy don't care how far you go<br/>
          I gave Him my ruin, He gave me rest<br/>
          Turns out He still knew what was best</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Final Chorus -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-heading font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-vor-gold-dark mb-3">Final Chorus</p>
          <p>I was lost in a town called Nowhere<br/>
          Every road led me back to despair<br/>
          But He lit the path, the narrow gate<br/>
          Tore down my pride and rebuilt my faith<br/>
          He called with mercy, He called with grace:<br/>
          <em>"Son, come and leave that broken place."</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-vor-charcoal text-white">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 text-center">
      <p class="font-heading text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
        Share this song with someone who needs to hear it.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="/music"
          class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full border-2 border-vor-gold text-vor-gold font-heading font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide hover:bg-vor-gold hover:text-vor-charcoal transition-all duration-200 no-underline"
        >
          More Music
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.youtube.com/@VoiceofRepentance"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-vor-gold-dark text-white font-heading font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide hover:bg-vor-gold transition-all duration-200 no-underline"
        >
          Subscribe on YouTube
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
